  {id: 1, text: 'Buy milk', completed: false},
  {id: 2, text: 'Do homework', completed: true}
]

WHY AN ARRAY?
- It can hold many tasks (not just one)
- We can add tasks, remove tasks, count tasks
- It keeps everything organized

ğŸ”§ THE TOOL: let arrayName = [];

SYNTAX:
let myList = [];  â† Creates an empty array
myList.push('item');  â† Adds an item to the array
myList.length  â† Tells you how many items
*/

