Recipe for "Make Coffee":
1. Boil water
2. Add coffee grounds
3. Pour water over grounds
4. Wait 4 minutes

You write this recipe ONCE, but can use it many times.

JavaScript function:
function makeCoffee() {
    boilWater();
    addGrounds();
    pourWater();
    wait(4);
}

Now whenever you need coffee, just call: makeCoffee();

ğŸ”§ FUNCTION SYNTAX:

function functionName() {
    // Code goes here
}

To use it: functionName();
*/

